channel.title: Help with lag for me...VERY strange
channel.description: Alright, I think i've posted this before...Well my server lags pretty bad for me at 16 people. I closed all other programs and deleted alot of stuff on my computer. The strange thing is that my computer wont lag for me on other servers even if it's at like 30-50 people. Help? Maybe someone give me a program or something to help reduce lag? Also, PLEASE DO NOT GIVE ME TIPS LIKE GET MORE RAM,MEMORY,AND STUFF LIKE THAT IM NOT INTERESTED IN THAT. Please and thank you :)
